---
import { Image } from "astro:assets"
import { Icon } from "astro-icon"
import avatarImg from "@/images/avatar.png"
---

<style>
  [astro-icon] {
    color: rgb(79, 70, 229);
  }
</style>

<aside>
  <h3 class="text-xl border-b-2 border-indigo-600 mt-0 pt-0">Profile</h3>
  <div class="text-center border border-indigo-600 rounded p-5">
    <figure class="mx-auto w-max">
      <Image
        src={avatarImg}
        alt="avatar"
        width="100"
        height="100"
        class="rounded-full"
      />
    </figure>
    <div class="p-4">
      <div class="text-xl">Loliver</div>
      <div class="flex justify-center">
        <p class="text-left mb-2">
          熊本の高専卒
          <br />
           毎週金曜はやる気・元気・無敵になる涼風青葉
          <br />
           ブログ活動もアイカツ！
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="flex justify-center gap-2">
        <a
          href="https://twitter.com/Lolitta_river"
          class="border rounded border-indigo-600 p-0.5"
        >
          <Icon name="fa-brands:twitter" />
        </a>
        <a
          href="https://loliver.hatenablog.jp/"
          class="border rounded border-indigo-600 p-0.5"
        >
          <Icon name="fa-brands:blogger" />
        </a>
        <a
          href="https://github.com/Loliver1224"
          class="border rounded border-indigo-600 p-0.5"
        >
          <Icon name="fa-brands:github" />
        </a>
        <a
          href="https://feedly.com/i/discover/sources/search/feed/https%3A%2F%2Fblog.loliver.net"
          class="border rounded border-indigo-600 p-0.5"
        >
          <Icon name="simple-icons:feedly" />
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</aside>
